        <updateDate>2005-04-06T19:05:07Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Safe Intersections Act of 2005 - Amends the Federal criminal code to prohibit the sale to, or use by, unauthorized users of traffic signal preemption transmitters (devices or mechanisms that can change a traffic signal's phase time or sequence). Sets forth both civil and criminal penalties for violations of such requirements.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
